  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Cut the egg rolls into bite-sized pieces and bake for 10 minutes.",
    "Heat the peanut oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and grated ginger to the skillet and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the shrimp to the skillet and cook until they are pink and fully cooked.",
    "Stir in the garam masala, salt, and lemon juice.",
    "Add the ferment-kimchi to the skillet and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "To assemble the chaat, divide the cooked shrimp mixture among individual mini cocottes.",
    "Top each cocotte with a piece of baked egg roll and a sprinkle of chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately."
  ],
